frameDefinitions: A Topical_entity has properties which are affected by the existence and association of an Entity.
The LUs in this frame describe the level that a Rate, or the variation in some quantity over a period of time, deviates from the norm.
An Event takes place at a Place and Time.
An Event with multiple Participants takes place.
An Item becomes filled with a Substance as a result of movement of liquid into visible or invisible interstices in the Item.
This frame is concerned with Cognizers remembering and forgetting mental Content.

The <fen>Cognizer</fen> is the person whose mental <fen>Content</fen> is at issue.

The <fen>Time</fen> is when the remembering or forgetting of mental <fen>Content</fen> occurs.
The <fen>Place</fen> is where the remembering or forgetting takes place.
